==English==

===Etymology===
From {{etyl|enm|en}} {{m|enm|weyfaren}}, originally in participle form {{m|enm|weyfarand}}, from {{etyl|ang|en}} {{m|ang|weġfarende||wayfaring}}, equivalent to {{compound|way|faring|lang=en}}. Cognate with {{cog|da|vejfarende||wayfaring}}, {{cog|sv|vägfarande|}}, {{cog|is|vegfarandi||wayfaring}}. More at {{l|en|way}}, {{l|en|fare}}.

